见，但病情十分严重，症状包括发烧、头痛、呕吐、腹泻和癫痫，约30%的感染者会死亡。马萨诸塞州政府也表示，从东部马脑炎疾病幸存下来的人往往会落下终身残疾，很少有人完全康复。美国发现罕见传染病例：死亡率达30%，4城镇紧急夜间封锁_牛津_东方_疾病"},"attached_info":"CkAI747F36uX2MBTEAMaCTExMDEyNzMyMSCh7q+2BjAAOIQBQARyCTY2NTMyMzc1MHgAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA","detail_text":"233 万热度","trend":0,"debut":true,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/v2-a14ee5910a20256f6ffde5117be3f04e_b.jpg"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"5_1724768310.114352","card_id":"Q_665408379","card_label":{"type":"hot","icon":"https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-266e83dbee46dce23b718e0531cb7d3a_1440w.png","night_icon":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-c89199839c237b87e52f010bb5e7d773_1440w.png"},"target":{"id":665408379,"title":"如何评价德约科维奇脖挂巴黎奥运会金牌出征美网？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/665408379","type":"question","created":1724721950,"answer_count":26,"follower_count":40,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[19753,62220,158301,3108869,3631481],"comment_count":0,"is_following":false,"excerpt":"[图片]"},"attached_info":"Cj8I747F36uX2MBTEAMaCTExMDE0NjEwOCCe1rS2BjAAOChABXIJNjY1NDA4Mzc5eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA=","detail_text":"184 万热度","trend":0,"debut":true,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/v2-05a46aa98d32ec2ae7e10bc262335c4a_b.jpg"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"6_1724768310.114619","card_id":"Q_665009055","card_label":{"type":"hot","icon":"https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-266e83dbee46dce23b718e0531cb7d3a_1440w.png","night_icon":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-c89199839c237b87e52f010bb5e7d773_1440w.png"},"target":{"id":665009055,"title":"如何看待《黑神话：悟空》里四妹被“鸡头”仙人捉去炼丹？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/665009055","type":"question","created":1724321680,"answer_count":38,"follower_count":76,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_